Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the support of someone I can rely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:31.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}toki ni tayoriaeru youna sonzai ni sasaerare{\i0}
